title: Are You Slowly Committing Suicide?
itunes:title: Are You Slowly Committing Suicide?
description:
How often do you think about the little, teeny, tiny decisions that you make? Because all too often, it is a compounding of those little decisions that propels you to success or kills you slowly. In this episode, we are going to talk about how to master those decisions.
